#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SYSCONFIG_LBL_FIELD_TASKS_COREUPDATE_INSTALL_HELP"
msgid "Do nothing: no action is taken. Send email: An email is sent, nothing is installed. Patch: Only patch versions (e.g. 1.2.<strong>3</strong> to 1.2.<strong>4</strong>) are installed; an email is sent otherwise. Minor: Only patch and minor versions (e.g. 1.<strong>2</strong>.x to 1.<strong>3</strong>.x) are installed; an email is sent otherwise. Any version: installs all updates, even if the major version changes (e.g. <strong>1</strong>.x to <strong>2</strong>.x)."
msgstr "Ничего не делать: никаких действий не предпринимается. Отправить письмо: отправляется письмо, ничего не устанавливается."

#, phpformat
