msgid "Number <code>0</code> (Sunday) to <code>6</code> (Saturday), contiguous range e.g. <code>1-5</code>, comma–separated list of values e.g. <code>1,3,5</code>, every day as <code>*</code>.<br> Instead of numbers you may use the abbreviated, three–letter, English names of the days of the week: <code>SUN</code>, <code>MON</code>, <code>TUE</code>, <code>WED</code>, <code>THU</code>, <code>FRI</code>, <code>SAT</code><br>A number followed by <code>L</code> for the last day of the week in the month, e.g. <code>5L</code> is the last Friday of the month.<br>Two numbers separated by <code>#</code> for n-th day of the week in the month, e.g. <code>5#3</code> is the 3rd Friday of the month."
msgstr "Число от <code>0</code> (воскресенье) до <code>6</code> (суббота), непрерывный диапазон или список."

