#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_USAGESTATS_LBL_INFO_BODY"
msgid "Akeeba Panopticon collects basic information about the environment it is executing in. This information is aggregated and helps us decide on which PHP and database server versions to support in future releases. From this page you can control whether this feature will be enabled, and review the information being sent to our server."
